{"tid":123140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人習慣咗啪手指","createTime":"2017-02-16T15:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T18:41:14.000Z","uid":1582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8135bbd613fa22dec00a4e9bc5aa0dfce9da9d","tid":123140,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"由細到大都啪<br />\n依家一啪勁大聲好爽<br />\n<br />\n腳指都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係點解有時膝頭都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af4a7085cf7a2ec52c8765c5da415c4546bf630","tid":123140,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"咁你要小心啲軟組織冇乜磨蝕晒"},{"pid":"101197d4a60b77733d593bfb5a34c5a52566c89a","tid":123140,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"腰都啪<br />\n頸又要啪"},{"pid":"472f259bb386a1f69c64bb662b88911060d021d7","tid":123140,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"小學日日啪而家啲手指關節好粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 永遠都唔會再啪手指<br />\n不過頸、腰、腳指、膝頭有時唔啪會唔舒服<br />\n到底點解"},{"pid":"511825bd0bedca1705c3a354d7cd6b1d68c33326","tid":123140,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"啪胸骨, 番唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"5f3e794a51bfaebc5248f13a2e094443cdb1e23f","tid":123140,"uid":46295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"好似話有空氣<br />\n啪左啲空氣冇左 就舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550ebdf6b96d764066f0494d2df2718ed6a1a796","tid":123140,"uid":23974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"上面講嘅都有啪開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢排中意啪鼻樑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05997bba4209ef311a9e5e7c5025b329d3a94a5","tid":123140,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啪胸骨, 番唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啪埋背脊由上到下 勁爽"},{"pid":"7b65b3ad5370586ac690a28634c46a90dd46d9bf","tid":123140,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"啪個下其實係爆炸黎<br />\n唔好笑住先<br />\n係新聞到剪出黎<br />\n<br />\n有人擔心是否骨頭碰撞磨擦的聲音，但實情是這種啪啪啪是氣壓造成。首先我們手指骨與骨的關節之間有空隙，裏頭注滿像蛋黃般的滑液（synovial fluid）。而當我們啪手指時，骨與骨之間的距離就會拉開，關節空隙體積大了，形成一個低壓區（low-pressure zone），而當中滑液裏的氣體，會慢慢形成一個大氣泡，直至周圍的滑液把這個氣泡卜的一聲擠破，而造成聲音。"},{"pid":"6416382336369af125c2190ce6be20ecd6d3ea8f","tid":123140,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"坐係凳到個身左右擰一下<br />\n腰同背發出嘞嘞聲既感覺<br />\n真係爽過打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb41ea127ecd36297a517fbd870d86a3bd9484df","tid":123140,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啪胸骨, 番唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啪埋背脊由上到下 勁爽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aaf8ee7378d207939befd275b1d65f66482b6ee","tid":123140,"uid":58076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote]啪胸骨, 番唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啪埋背脊由上到下 勁爽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quot胸骨間唔中啪，會痛，好少再試<br />\n反而頸成日啪，一野拎過去好撚爽，但唔知係咪做得多依家仲易攰加會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又爽到戒唔到"},{"pid":"3df768b2f5b312e27e5f658b619b32bd1ede97b5","tid":123140,"uid":53118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐係凳到個身左右擰一下<br />\n腰同背發出嘞嘞聲既感覺<br />\n真係爽過打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由上至下連住咁啪落去個下 真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ee108f3a296264ab95ed02a20948d756df1d4c","tid":123140,"uid":16390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面講嘅都有啪開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢排中意啪鼻樑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啪鼻樑係點啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴線"},{"pid":"e2dcf76acc20480adebdea7e96c8500bae485ccb","tid":123140,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"d手指會又粗又短,但又戒唔到......."},{"pid":"f51ce089d9b229b3739684ab4b8556809551a21c","tid":123140,"uid":16712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:41:14.000Z","msg":"好中意啪腰、頸、腳腕同膝頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啪到好似越黎越攰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇巴打知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}